definition: abbr. for 青海[Qing1 hai3], Qinghai Province

sentences.english: The town featured a rich history, and was well-known for its culture and traditions along its canals.
sentences.chinese: 青浦历史悠久，以运河文化和传统闻名。

sentences.english: The second chapter considers the necessity of developing vacation tourist products in Qingpu District.
sentences.chinese: 第二部分是青浦区开发度假旅游产品的必然性阐述。

sentences.english: On your way back, you will pass Shanghai Qingpu Outlets, where you can do some shopping.
sentences.chinese: 返程途中经过上海青浦奥特莱斯，你可以去那里购物。

sentences.english: Hope you'll visit Qingpu again soon.
Jinshang Highway, Qingpu, near Grand View Garden.
sentences.chinese: 金商公路708号，青浦区，近大观园。

sentences.english: How far is it from Qingpu to Zhujiajiao? About 15 minutes by bus.
sentences.chinese: 青浦到朱家角有多远？乘公车大概15分钟。

sentences.english: Toshiki International Corp. ( Shanghai ) was established in 1999, with the location in the Qingpu Industrial Area, Shanghai .
sentences.chinese: 公司成立于1999年，座落于上海青浦工业园区。

sentences.english: Shall I book a room in Qingpu Hotel for you?
sentences.chinese: 要我帮预订青浦宾馆吗？

sentences.english: Qingpu, a land of fish and rice, lies in the west suburbs of Shanghai.
sentences.chinese: 青浦是一个鱼米之乡，位于上海的西郊。

sentences.english: The other stations are in Qingpu, Jiading, Nanhui and Pudong.
sentences.chinese: 其余的加油站分别在青浦，嘉定，南汇和浦东。

sentences.english: Production base is located in Qingpu, with offices in urban areas, and convenient transportation.
sentences.chinese: 生产基地设在青浦，市区有办事处，交通方便。

sentences.english: The third chapter is about the development of detailed vacation tourist products.
sentences.chinese: 第三部分是青浦区具体要开发的度假旅游产品。

definition: Jiading district of northwest Shanghai/final reign name 1208-1224 of South Song emperor Ningzong 寧宗|宁宗[Ning2 zong1]
Nanhui former district of Shanghai, now in Pudong New District 浦東新區|浦东新区[Pu3 dong1 xin1 qu1], Shanghai

Chuansha, name of street and park in Pudong New District 浦東新區|浦东新区[Pu3 dong1 xin1 qu1], Shanghai
Pudong New District, subprovincial district of Shanghai
the main river through Shanghai/name of a district in Shanghai
